The following implementation will focus on building a data processing backend using Node.js, which can handle high-volume data processing both in batch and real-time modes. 

### Data Processor Implementation Plan

This project will include the following components:
1. **Models** to define the data structure.
2. **Routes** to handle different types of data processing requests.
3. **Services** to handle the actual data processing logic.

Below is the implementation:

